reviews.text:
i mixed this up on the 16th this month and its pretty tasty! i like the Espresso, Cookie Dough and Milk &amp; Honey combo a lot.What it lacks for me is the Creamy milky part but it's still good! ill let it steep and comeback later :-)&#xD;
&#xD;
EDIT: tbh, i thought it would change a lot. After almost 4 Weeks it didnt change much and what i get now is pretty much burned Espresso with cream. I think this is definitely not a long steeper. Best spot is around 1-2 weeks. Still thx for the inspiration!
